If, for any reason, you are unable to update Stella Mod using the Launcher, please uninstall the current version and install the new one from the official website.

data.name: Default_HiThereItLooksLikeWereSeeinEachOtherForTheFirstTime
data.value:
Hi there! It looks like we're seeing each other for the first time! Please take a moment to review the terms of use and the guidelines for this software to avoid any potential issues. The documentation is available on our official website. By using Stella Mod, you agree to the terms outlined in the documentation.
This software is continuously supported by the developer thanks to Stella Mod Plus subscribers. The revenue helps cover the costs of fiber-optic internet and electricity bills. The API server is hosted in a private home in Poland, which means the local administrator is the sole owner of the database. Genshin Stella Mod prioritizes user privacy and security - no analytical or hardware data is ever sent without your consent.
Stella Mod is safe software, so there's nothing to worry about. Just remember not to use cheats in the game. If you need help, feel free to join our Discord server or contact us at contact@sefinek.net.
Please also note that Stella Mod is completely independent and NOT affiliated in ANY way with HoYoverse. If you like this project, consider supporting its further development by subscribing to Stella Mod Plus.
Thanks, and see you in the game! Have fun.
